{"tid":17874,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[支那]載20人巴士墮湖 最少18死","createTime":"2016-12-02T03:53:03.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-02T04:39:52.000Z","uid":122,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2e2b84fe0217a4033087dc295dc08fd5522e247e","tid":17874,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T03:53:04.000Z","msg":"<strong>【慘烈車禍】載20人巴士墮湖 最少18死</strong><br />\n<br />\n2016-12-02 11:36:00 HKT<br />\n<br />\n湖北發生嚴重巴士意外，今早大約6時，一輛從鄂州開往武漢的巴士衝入路邊湖泊，初步了解巴士上載有約20人。據當地交通運輸部門相關負責人透露，已造成18人死亡，另有2人正在醫院搶救。據最新消息指，鄂州警方已扣留司機，事故原因正在調查中。"},{"pid":"30ff3c73a2b361a4a697ee09aecd9cf6c0cdb848","tid":17874,"uid":20241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T04:23:47.000Z","msg":"個司機無死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35e7ca91492863ecf9236044be597aef25edb097","tid":17874,"uid":4525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T04:39:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}